high_descs: move to the right of the sink to the counter
pick up an apple from the counter
move to the sink to the left
clean the apple in the sink
move to the table behind you
put the apple on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the right to face the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the apple from the counter.
Move to the left to face the sink.
Place the apple in the sink, fill it up with water, and pick up the apple.
Turn around then go straight to face the brown kitchen table.
Place the apple on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed off apple on the brown kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter, face the apple on the counter to the left.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn left, bring the apple to the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Turn around with the cleaned apple and bring it to the round dining table on the left, next to the fridge.
Put the cleaned apple on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed apple on the table.
